gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 126, Raptors 119
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Raptors, 126-119. Jordan Clarkson (30 points, six assists, four 3PM) and Lauri Markkanen (30 points, nine rebounds, five assists, four 3PM) combined for 60 points for the Jazz in the victory, while Scottie Barnes tallied 32 points, 14 rebounds and seven assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Jazz have won back-to-back games as they improve to 12-18 on the season, while the Raptors fall to 11-18.
